  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>If you'd like an opportunity to have a face-to-face chat with one of our team members, you can request a video call appointment. We'd be more than happy to talk with you about your next trip and answer any questions you may have before committing to book. We're on hand to give expert advice on our trips and destinations, and to make booking your next ski holiday, summer break or Lapland adventure as easy as possible. </p>
<p>Our video calls are easy to set up and simple to use. To book your video call:</p>
<ol>
<li><span>Pick a date and time that suits you</span></li>
<li><span>Fill out the form with your details</span></li>
<li><span>We’ll send you an email to confirm your appointment and share the video link </span></li>
<li><span>When it's time for your call, just click on the link in your email and you’ll be joined by an Inghams team member</span><span></span></li>
</ol>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>VIDEO LINK</span></p>]]></bodyText>
